(2x)^{2013} + (2y)^{2013} + (2z)^{2013} =3 
xy + yz + zx + 2xyz = 1.
x=\frac{a}{2}, y=\frac{b}{2}, z=\frac{c}{2}
ab+bc+ca+abc=4, a^{2013}+b^{2013}+c^{2013}=3
\geq
4=ab+bc+ca+abc \geq 3\sqrt[3]{a^2b^2c^2}+abc
x=\sqrt[3]{abc}
4 \geq 3x^2+x^3
(x-1)(x+2)^2 \leq 0
x \leq 1
abc \leq 1
ab+ac+bc=4-abc \geq 3
a^2+b^2+c^2 \geq ab+ac+bc
\frac{1}{2}((a-b)^2+(b-c)^2+(c-a)^2) \geq 0
1=\sqrt[2013]{\frac{a^{2013}+b^{2013}+c^{2013}}{3}} \geq \sqrt{\frac{a^2+b^2+c^2}{3}} \geq \sqrt{\frac{ab+bc+ca}{3}} \geq 1
a=b=c
3=3a^{2013}
a=b=c=1
(x, y, z)=(\frac{1}{2}, \frac{1}{2}, \frac{1}{2})
